<div id="pf11ce" class="pf w2a h124" data-page-no="11ce"><div class="pc pc11ce w2a h124"><div class="t me35 x17 hc4 y1a87 ff1 fs3b fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Studies in the Revelation </div><div class="t m143 x61 h28 y1645 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SENIOR DIVISION, THIRD QUARTER, 1918 </div><div class="t m20fe x9b h30 y169c ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Introductory Note </div><div class="t m2372 x4a h4 y1c8c ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This remarkable book of prophecy is often called &quot;the </div><div class="t m1f9c x92 h4 y1f09 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Apocalypse,&quot; a word meaning revelation, disclosure, unfold-</div><div class="t m1950 x92 h4 y1f9e ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ment. As the opening words say, it is a revelation of Jesus </div><div class="t mb89 x92 h4 y1439 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Christ, given Him by God, and transmitted through the angel </div><div class="t m11ad x92 h4 y1ecb ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to the prophet John. </div><div class="t m9a1 x4a h13 y1172 ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">WRITER: </div><div class="t me18 x12 h4 y1172 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">John the beloved apostle. </div><div class="t mb6c x4a h13 y1bca ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">TIME: </div><div class="t mf6c x83 h4 y1bca ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Probably </div><div class="t m271 x40 h13 y1bca ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A. </div><div class="t me7d xa4 h4 y1bca ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">D. 96 or 97. </div><div class="t m1018 x4a h4 y18c3 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">PLACE: The visions were given on the barren, rocky is-</div><div class="t m1285 x92 h4 y1f58 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">land of Patmos, about fifteen miles in circumference, in the </div><div class="t m110e x92 h4 y1996 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">JEgean Sea, which the Roman empire used as a place of ban-</div><div class="t m1554 x92 h4 y638 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ishment, and where John had been exiled by the emperor </div><div class="t m9b3 x82 h26 y1698 ff1 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">MODERN PATMOS </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
